title: 170: Advanced Smart Training Techniques
description: Justin is out of town so Sal and Adam take advantage of his absence to talk about body building and training for aesthetics. They start with a follow up to yesterday's episode with Joe Donnelly and then go into depth on advanced training techniques and how to train smart for maximum results.
